goals.complete: We're on the right track, but the twins won't stop bickering. If they'd just work together, they could be an amazing team.

goals.active: Report to Trahearne at the Grove.
goals.complete: Our path is clear, but only one twin will be assisting me. The two got in a huge fight, and refused to work together. If all sylvari acted like this, we'd never have built the Grove!
